<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">Legal</div>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="hero-sub">Effective date: 1 April 2026 &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; Covers GDPR, PDPL, DPDP Act 2023, UAE Data Law</div>
</div>
<div class="content">
  <div class="highlight"><strong>Key facts:</strong> We collect only what is necessary to operate the service. We never sell your data. You can request deletion at any time. Data is stored on Railway infrastructure (EU/US region) with encryption at rest.</div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>1. Data We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Account data</h3>
    <p>Name, email address, phone number, role, company name. Collected when you register or are added by your Company Admin.</p>
    <h3>HSE operational data</h3>
    <p>Incidents, NCRs, actions, audit records, toolbox talks, and other HSE records you create within the Platform. This data belongs to you and your company.</p>
    <h3>Usage data</h3>
    <p>Page views, feature usage, login timestamps, and IP addresses. Used for security monitoring and product improvement only.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To provide and operate the SafetyPro AI platform</li>
      <li>To send incident and escalation notifications via email and WhatsApp</li>
      <li>To generate HSE analytics and reports within your account</li>
      <li>To diagnose technical issues when you request support (with your approval)</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not use your data for advertising, third-party marketing, or AI model training.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share your data only with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">Railway</strong> — cloud hosting (servers in EU/US)</li>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">SendGrid (Twilio)</strong> — email delivery</li>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and DDoS protection</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All sub-processors are bound by data processing agreements. We do not share data with any other third parties.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data (right to erasure)</li>
      <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
      <li>Object to processing in certain circumstances</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Submit requests to: <strong style="color:var(--blue);">privacy@safetyproworld.com</strong>. We respond within 30 days.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Active account data is retained for the duration of your subscription. On account termination, data is retained for 30 days for export, then permanently deleted. Audit logs are retained for 5 years to comply with regulatory requirements.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>6. Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security including HTTPS encryption in transit, encryption at rest, JWT-based authentication, role-based access control, and audit logging of all privileged access. We are working towards ISO 27001 certification.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>7. Regional Compliance</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">EU/UK:</strong> GDPR / UK GDPR — we act as Data Processor. DPA available on request.</li>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">India:</strong> DPDP Act 2023 — we follow data fiduciary obligations.</li>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">Saudi Arabia:</strong> PDPL — data transfers comply with PDPL cross-border requirements.</li>
      <li><strong style="color:var(--t1);">UAE:</strong> DIFC/ADGM data protection frameworks where applicable.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
    <p>Data Protection queries: <strong style="color:var(--blue);">privacy@safetyproworld.com</strong></p>
  </div>
